# Grafana
- For the visualization of the data metrics of our application we use Grafana.
- Grafana works on port 3000 by default.

# How do we create a Grafana dashboard?
- We add datasources and create dashboards

- Prometheus server URL --> http://my-prometheus-server.monitoring.svc.cluster.local:80

- command for Grafana password --> kubectl get secret (grafana_secret) -n (namespace_of_grafana) -o jsonpath="{.data.admin-password}" | base64 --decode ; echo

username - admin
password - prom-operator